{"tid":1137664,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] LAST IDEA ラストイデア (59) 拍賣請假平假名搜尋 VIP暫時未開 SE食屎","createTime":"2019-05-04T03:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T10:51:00.000Z","uid":44828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"03c1ccf3173a05c91dae134a793b08998fea97ea","tid":1137664,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kT89CVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkT89CVU.jpg&h=77691165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方網站 : <a href=\"https://www.lastidea.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lastidea.jp%2F&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=c059ead8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lastidea.jp/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lastidea_rpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flastidea_rpg&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=ae126c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lastidea_rpg</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6SmH9mR82nj28_NNg_rZvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC6SmH9mR82nj28_NNg_rZvA&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW9%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=9c134c0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6SmH9mR82nj28_NNg_rZvA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">官方上Famitsu果陣話《LAST IDEA》係平成跨越時代既神驚</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲簡介</span></span></strong><br />\n  SQUARE ENIX 旗下智慧型手機新作《LAST IDEA》於官方生放送中宣布，遊戲將於 2019 年 4 月 18 日（傍晚）正式上市。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zabvnrp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZabvnrp.jpg&h=1c328222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《LAST IDEA》是一隻冒險尋寶動作 RPG 手機遊戲，玩家扮演一位新手尋寶獵人，與失憶的少女一起展開冒險旅程。遊戲不設轉蛋完素，家可以按照等級在「Treasure hunt」獲得各種裝備，透過升級技能強化自己能力，就連最強的裝備也可以在「Treasure hunt」之中獲得，遊戲打寶元素非常豐富。主打輕鬆操作的割草玩法。值得一提的是，本作搭載了全新開發的操作系統「SMACOMA（Smart Command）」，透過滑動、點擊等直覺上的操作，任何人都能輕鬆享受遊戲流暢的打擊感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2Us87B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2Us87B.jpg&h=f025b153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chGvnui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchGvnui.jpg&h=1920d81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4h6Fsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4h6Fsf.jpg&h=a5808931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 遊戲特色</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">無轉蛋的尋寶 RPG</span></span></strong><br />\n營運團隊指出，《LAST IDEA》不存在所謂的「角色轉蛋」或是「裝備轉蛋」。玩家只能透過尋寶獲得符合等級的裝備，並且磨練玩家技能來變得更加強大，而遊戲中最高級的裝備也只能透過尋寶獲得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45od4Gy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45od4Gy.jpg&h=2fadf1bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7pwRmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7pwRmz.jpg&h=aad0cab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SqspGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SqspGz.jpg&h=4d7bcbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">高自由度的自定義角色</span></span></strong><br />\n遊戲初期實裝的裝備超過 600 種，每件裝備都能透過尋寶獲得並賦予其隨機的效果（屬性）及性能，即便是相同名稱的裝備持有的特性也不見相同。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uV4rVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uV4rVp.jpg&h=282fae80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8id4Hc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8id4Hc.jpg&h=6ab75638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  玩家在推進故事的過程中將遇到被稱為「IDEA（イデア）」的角色，可以透過「IDEA」從 10 種以上的技能樹中學習 3 種技能，並將其設置成可操作角色。從體型、髮型、角色聲音、裝備到技能樹都可以自行組合搭配，養成符合自己喜好的角色。<br />\n（※裝備的稀有度包括 Normal、Magic、Rare、Epic、Legend 等等；技能樹則有劍、炎、弓、盾、雷、死靈、斧、槍、雙刀、冰等超過 10 種類型。）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdpHX2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdpHX2j.jpg&h=4f7abde6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">佢唔似白貓龍絆抽左個角色就定晒形，佢主打自由組合技能樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如原本劍skill 可以裝備雙手闊劍，再學斧 skill 剛力可以單手拎闊劍，再學雙刀 skill 變拎雙闊劍<br />\n或者學雙刀+火+雷就會幫左右雙刀附火附雷<br />\n唔單止外形有變，技能都有變，例如弓+槍可以變每支箭都貫通，弓+雙刀可以射到人出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">By<span style=\"color: blue;\">有翅膀的黑貓</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D4XYSx-UcAAtV-W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD4XYSx-UcAAtV-W.jpg&h=e266c086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">以直覺操作的流暢戰鬥系統「SMACOMA」</span></span></strong><br />\n本作搭載了全新開發的操作系統「SMACOMA（Smart Command）」，透過滑動、點擊等直覺上的操作，任何人都能輕鬆享受遊戲流暢的打擊感。此外，玩家可以自行設置指定動作施放想使用的技能，以最習慣的配置打倒敵人，體驗以直覺操作的戰鬥系統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L95W2u0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL95W2u0.jpg&h=30ee3b92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4 人同時遊玩 &amp; 全玩家參與的拍賣會</span></span></strong><br />\n製作團隊指出，玩家可以招募其他同伴，前往高難度地城或是藏寶地點中尋找沉睡的「貴重寶物」。與同伴們發現的稀有裝備除了自己使用之外，還可以透過由全玩家參加的拍賣會賺取大筆金錢，而遊戲內獲得的裝備幾乎都能至拍賣會進行買賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhc6Fg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffhc6Fg3.jpg&h=4aa689c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BfHndB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBfHndB4.jpg&h=465d2c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">全語音動畫享受故事劇情</span></span></strong><br />\n配合本作主線故事的行進過程，官方也會隨時更新故事的演出動畫，將邀請到實力堅強的豪華聲優陣容，以全語音的方式展開本作的動畫劇情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBUT4Ky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBUT4Ky.jpg&h=c9b88351&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34fd10ce97513d63596406731542e4fc9c1f2d3","tid":1137664,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"屌你打錯字"},{"pid":"2021c38352dc5baf52df0aabb05d20906e6c4720","tid":1137664,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f81bfcce128bccd51870776ebc6875c9778606","tid":1137664,"uid":60720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:36:34.000Z","msg":"你地用咩技打落我個草人到<br />\n我頭先見到一堆99999傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RanXT8i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRanXT8i.png&h=d48fcc32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"998ff1501947d3f2fa9daef3faf7aa09295dac31","tid":1137664,"uid":73626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581302c01436d47e1e059c06a63f8ff5b485b97f","tid":1137664,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開過"},{"pid":"6e7e44de598e4f450410a5a0e8b2db93153cb5bf","tid":1137664,"uid":135211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n正常用拍賣 而