d":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"賤巴萬巴入黎1回先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"你地用咩技打落我個草人到<br />\n我頭先見到一堆99999傷<br />\nDps上90幾萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"唔好問我 我最低dps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能係死靈自爆？maya巴斧爆？"},{"pid":"fef85d41167ff1436a25c4c7c53a18f8b3093b86","tid":1137664,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:42:53.000Z","msg":"拍賣會唔會加速隻 game死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30f708421a703511d78859f92cf464566b3aa1e","tid":1137664,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"兩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f621c13aa73715895157fd90ac3b6f45e95c9d91","tid":1137664,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"推依邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c463fd3f07d4eeb4972c455e20142aba457263d","tid":1137664,"uid":116748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}